description:
Single family 1942 Craftsman Bungalow in residential neighborhood seeking short term renter. Note: Photos taken before renovations due to occupancy.

Features: 
- 1 full bath (photo currently unavailable);
- Hardwood Floors in all rooms except kitchen;
- Gas/Electric Hookups for laundry onsite in garage;
- Attached garage with bonus room and carport;
- Pets allowed with additional deposit (note: certain breeds prohibited per home insurance. Please inquire);
- Front yard and spacious backyard, both covered and uncovered (photos limited due to occupancy);
- Livable Area: 777 Sq Ft., Lot size 4,959 Sq. Ft.
- Blocks from grocery, restaurants and bay - Roseville area of Point Loma, San Diego.

Property can be shown by appointment only. Please reply via e-mail if interested. Must be open to short term rental.
